# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
# ✅ Changed JWT_SECRET and JWT_REFRESH_SECRET to new random values
# ✅ Changed DATABASE_PASSWORD to strong password (if using external DB)
# ✅ Updated MAIL_* settings with your SMTP service
# ✅ Updated FRONTEND_URL to your production domain
